le\u2019s\nmistakes.\nPoloniu\u2019s advice to John L. Lewis:\n\u201cThe friends thou hast and their\nadoption tried, grapple them to thee\nwith hooks of steel.\u201d\nWHY\ndoe* the U. S. Goyenunant require\nPASTEURIZATION\nfor all Milk need by the Army, ba\neluding all training eampe.\nARE THEY WRONG?\nLAREDO CREAMERY COMPANY\nQearta\u2014lie with coupon* Tei. Ml\nFROM NEW YORK\nAND EASTETRN POINTS\nShip Via:\nLONE STAR\nPACKAGE CAR\nCarp MORGAN LINE\n5","height":"20444","width":"15360"}}
